{"tid":1457772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警唔清場＝散水撚錯；黑警清場＝留守撚錯","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:26:22.000Z","uid":90601,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8f3f65a525489a18b94347cddaea07a13015fc","tid":1457772,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"但點解無人留意到<br />\n今日所有成功令航班停飛 直接影響香港對外交通<br />\n而且無任何衝突 所有想走既人成功撤退<br />\n聽日中外媒一定有報&ldquo;黑警811暴力引致癱瘓機場&ldquo;<br />\n已造做到和理非最想要既國際聲音<br />\n有咩咁錯？ 點解要互屌？<br />\n<br />\n真正既錯係咩？<br />\n唔係無清場而散水<br />\n或者留守左而唔散水俾人打到仆街<br />\n最錯既係，我地俾人打到仆街，但影響唔到政府<br />\n<br />\n大家都成功達到目的<br />\n無人有錯，無人需要道歉呀唔該你地"},{"pid":"74b78312d56084dd78b79de78cb35e4000c547dd","tid":1457772,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"錯手負皮咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f23be80d2a759a441427b6b59576e6066fb167f","tid":1457772,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb54d4ea8b02ac64be0fc7d455dcdcf6d6cf656f","tid":1457772,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:15:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52b4b4d7ae4edb95b507a1497b979b502d13aca3","tid":1457772,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:15:11.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5cd8b96a769c6fe1b1ad899ac10b027cfde54832","tid":1457772,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8e5c04e810acb31cb249b49b870c05da6b9e3a0","tid":1457772,"uid":78666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:15:40.000Z","msg":"最錯係3毛分化撚"},{"pid":"1eec8cca1429e61ef8a6e5e1a192d1672279eca3","tid":1457772,"uid":53570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite