0Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da79458984f13e86fbf918fb862080b4c658a93f","tid":1457772,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:20:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">讀稿位係陷阱<br />\n讀稿位係陷阱<br />\n讀稿位係陷阱</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推到唔俾佢哋讀到稿！<br />\n<br />\n一定要咁 KEEP住要咁！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>萬人一推所有記者瘋狂插問追問721 811 唔俾仆街政府讀稿政治宣傳！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457037</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該幫手推個POST"},{"pid":"8b3a77a6b2fa0bbde5be1b899fe35eded76c4e01","tid":1457772,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fff0c6233bc11f2d46f246c00e21574d75af13ec","tid":1457772,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"商界最怕一樣嘢，就係估你唔到（uncertainty）。任何一樣嘢長期發生就必定估到（certainty)，商界就會有對策。因此，連續N日令機場癱瘓、連續佔領道路等行動對商界個影響冇突發性癱瘓機場咁金。如果N日冇機場，商界可以安排車隊，如果N日塞路，商界可以改路。但如果有機場但又唔知幾時要關閉，咁就效應大。效應要大必要估你唔到。<br />\n<br />\nWater嘅形態正正係估佢唔到。<br />\n<br />\nBe water。<br />\n<br />\n經濟手段好撚有用，一定要繼續！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ecf5b7c2e9bdaf1cc4c4b19c39da86e586cdeb27","tid":1457772,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"415a99564aab1a5068a1e82fd2cb20083c8ba8df","tid":1457772,"uid":112101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee8585170398b2f3ff1bcfeb1c65860ef561152","tid":1457772,"uid":265197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"無得咁計<br />\n黑警見多人<br />\n咪唔敢清<br />\n見散晒水<br />\n咪入黎搞搞震<br />\n散水黨不嬲都有<br />\n重點係有人相信<br />\n而家愈黎愈多武力衝突愈黎愈無底線<br />\n又黑社會又斬人又爆眼爆頭<br />\n令到人心惶惶<br />\n但要諗清楚如果機場內放tg<br />\n就唔再係單純政府話ok就ok嫁喇<br />\n人地嘅乘客萬一經過機場有對催淚彈過敏癮狀<br />\n到時責任係機場定航空公司揹先"},{"pid":"4bb2a17f4f50013ab8629c3916aeb7207f733eb0","tid":1457772,"uid":258346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"After"},{"pid":"d0ac1ae30f42b50014fece757835c75233577fb2","tid":1457772,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad644957a01442129a3071e57fda848ff50a7d0","tid":1457772,"uid":16762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6345ddad678ff7c27f360f8b2dc456a20ee7a989","tid":1457772,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"分化撚大勝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"所以見分化撚即Block"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"啲人仲係度和應緊分化撚係度屌鳩人散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}